Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
program: A030102(n) = { my(r=[n%3]); while(0<n\=3, r=concat(n%3, r)); subst(Polrev(r),x,3); } \\ After _M. F. Hasler_'s Nov 04 2011 code in A030102.
A263273 = n -> if(!n,n,A030102(n/(3^valuation(n,3))) * (3^valuation(n, 3))); \\ Taking of the quotient probably unnecessary.
A064989(n) = {my(f); f = factor(n); if((n>1 && f[1,1]==2), f[1,2] = 0); for (i=1, #f~, f[i,1] = precprime(f[i,1]-1)); factorback(f)};
